title: WVU vs. Baylor Game Preview Special
text: Written by Joe Brocato Created on October 15, 2015 @ 5:13PM (broadcast will air on WVFX Fox 10 Saturday from 11:30-12:00... or you can watch it right here now... that's cool too). * Recap of the 2014 WVU-Baylor game * A look at how WVU will move ahead without Karl Joseph * Key matchups * Conversation with WVU senior punter Nick O'Toole * Catching up with former MHS & WVU LB Tyler Anderson Share
